== Personal life ==
His older sister Rikke was a very talented handball player at top level, but had to suspend her career at the age of 23 due to her many knee injuries.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nrk.no/sport/rikke-greide-ikke-a-fortelle-at-hun-hadde-lagt-opp.-hun-var-midt-i-en-identitetskrise-1.15289935|title=Rikke greide ikke å fortelle at hun hadde lagt opp. Hun var midt i en identitetskrise|website=[[NRK]]|date=2 February 2021|access-date=16 October 2023}}</ref>

